        "content": "<div style=\"font-family:'Inter',-apple-system,system-ui,sans-serif;padding:24px 28px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#0F172A 0%,#0B1220 100%);border-radius:14px;color:#F8FAFC;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;gap:32px;align-items:start;border:1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.25);\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#CBD5E1;border-left:4px solid #38BDF8;padding-left:18px;margin:0;\">From a conversation, you can walk down to the trace that produced it, the tool the model called, the database it queried, the error on Postgres, and the SQL itself.<span style=\"display:block;margin-top:14px;color:#38BDF8;font-weight:700;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;\">Observability is the control plane for AI systems.</span></p>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;min-width:200px;\">\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px;background:#1E293B;border:1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.30);\"><span style=\"width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:6px;display:inline-grid;place-items:center;font-size:14px;background:rgba(56,189,248,0.15);color:#38BDF8;\">&#128172;</span><span style=\"font-family:ui-monospace,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.10em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#F8FAFC;\">Conversation</span></div>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;place-items:center;height:12px;color:#475569;font-size:12px;\">&#x25BC;</div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px;background:#1E293B;border:1px solid rgba(138,184,255,0.30);\"><span style=\"width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:6px;display:inline-grid;place-items:center;font-size:14px;background:rgba(138,184,255,0.15);color:#8AB8FF;\">&#129517;</span><span style=\"font-family:ui-monospace,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.10em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#F8FAFC;\">Trace</span></div>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;place-items:center;height:12px;color:#475569;font-size:12px;\">&#x25BC;</div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px;background:#1E293B;border:1px solid rgba(167,139,250,0.30);\"><span style=\"width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:6px;display:inline-grid;place-items:center;font-size:14px;background:rgba(167,139,250,0.15);color:#A78BFA;\">&#128736;</span><span style=\"font-family:ui-monospace,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.10em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#F8FAFC;\">Tool call</span></div>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;place-items:center;height:12px;color:#475569;font-size:12px;\">&#x25BC;</div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px;background:#1E293B;border:1px solid rgba(244,114,182,0.30);\"><span style=\"width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:6px;display:inline-grid;place-items:center;font-size:14px;background:rgba(244,114,182,0.15);color:#F472B6;\">&#9888;</span><span style=\"font-family:ui-monospace,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.10em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#F8FAFC;\">DB error</span></div>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;place-items:center;height:12px;color:#475569;font-size:12px;\">&#x25BC;</div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px;background:#1E293B;border:1px solid rgba(251,146,60,0.30);\"><span style=\"width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:6px;display:inline-grid;place-items:center;font-size:14px;background:rgba(251,146,60,0.15);color:#FB923C;\">&#119826;</span><span style=\"font-family:ui-monospace,monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.10em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#F8FAFC;\">SQL</span></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n"
      }
    },
